{"id": 1766, "genre": 1000, "title": "你是哪一种主题公园or游乐场玩家？", "description": "各种各样的主题公园，你都是怎么个玩法？", "record_count": 8608, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170629021315Vr8lKRjWaCnwPT6U.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-29T17:00:41Z", "questions": [{"id": 2514, "title": "你是哪一种主题公园or游乐场玩家？", "content": "你是哪一种主题公园玩家？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 216929, "content": "追求刺激型，知道方圆几百里哪儿的过山车轨道最陡", "image": "img/option/option/20170628201153D2dgxh3UZRqviPBe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216930, "content": "拍照为主型，把游乐场当做一个大型写真集地", "image": "img/option/option/20170628201319QZLs3b1Dgr5F0duq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216932, "content": "旋转木马型，大型游乐设备都不太敢玩，会参加一些轻松的项目", "image": "img/option/option/20170628201447nxtUJXMQe52rbuEa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216933, "content": "科技爱好者，会被噱头型VR、AR元素吸引", "image": "img/option/option/201706290209051eLfkSWKZYUh7jB5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216934, "content": "文艺系，对动漫和电影相关的感兴趣", "image": "img/option/option/20170629020820NwvpaCrnEPBIcdkF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216936, "content": "机智的错峰出游型，只买夜场票或者工作日去", "image": "img/option/option/20170629020642WGx3Cjkoicn7tH2s.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216937, "content": "策略型，擅长用同样的时间安排好先后顺序，玩比别人多的项目", "image": "img/option/option/20170629020506kxMuvZjQgi43tSE8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216938, "content": "集邮型，所有项目都要玩到，甚至不惜住在附近住好几天", "image": "img/option/option/20170629015521KVisblEhU3eGmBD1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216939, "content": "道具型，买各种纪念品，披挂一身，特别high特别投入", "image": "img/option/option/20170629015338nGa4zUxFfOeokL6l.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 216940, "content": "本人是道具型，根本不玩，主要是帮忙拿东西，拍照", "image": "img/option/option/201706290150423jr7kyBJX4QuaIot.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}